From f5df4f6fea9299aaeaaadab73250912134de83b1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: patch <patch@local>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 15:18:31 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: remove explanatory copy from Combat page, simplify
 Compare empty state

- Combat evaluator: removed the intro paragraph explaining multipliers
  and the dual in-sector/out-of-sector model. Heading and the rest of
  the page (side pickers, results, 'How this model works' details)
  are untouched.
- Compare page empty state simplified per request: 'Nothing to compare
  yet. Build a ship load out then press compare to add it to the
  comparison table.'
