 src/views/CombatView.tsx  | 5 -----
 src/views/CompareView.tsx | 2 +-
 2 files changed, 1 insertion(+), 6 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/views/CombatView.tsx b/src/views/CombatView.tsx
