-        Pit two builds against each other — with multipliers, so "20 torpedo-less bombers vs 1 Asgard" is one dropdown away.
-        Estimates use two different models because X4 does: fully simulated <b>in-sector</b> fights and the statistical
-        <b> out-of-sector</b> resolution. Directional estimates, not gospel — see "How this model works" below.
-      </p>
       <div className="csides">
         <SidePicker data={data} roles={roles} side="A" spec={a} onChange={setA} />
         <div className="vs">VS</div>
diff --git a/src/views/CompareView.tsx b/src/views/CompareView.tsx
